# Landing Page YML Generation Rules

## File Naming and Structure
- **File Extension**: `.yml` (not .yaml)
- **Naming Convention**: lowercase with underscores (e.g., `miami-coding-bootcamp.es.yml`)
- **Language Support**: Both English (`.us.yml`) and Spanish (`.es.yml`) versions required
- **Location**: Files must be saved in `src/data/landing/`

## Required Top-Level Sections

### meta_info (Required)
- `slug`: URL slug for the landing page
- `title`: Browser tab title and SEO title
- `description`: Meta description (under 160 characters)
- `image`: Social media preview image (use existing image routes)
- `keywords`: SEO keywords (none by default)
- `visibility`: "visible" (default), "hidden", or "unlisted"
- `template`: Must be "landing_a"
- `redirects`: Array of URL redirections
- `utm_course`: Array of course slugs ["full-stack", "software-engineering", "machine-learning-engineering"]
- `utm_location`: Array of location slugs (see supported locations below)
- `automation`: Default "soft"
- `tag`: Default "request_more_info"

### form (Required)
- `fields`: Array of form fields ["first_name", "last_name", "full_name", "phone", "email"]
- `heading`: Form title
- `motivation`: Form subtitle/motivation text
- `button_label`: Submit button text
- `redirect`: Optional redirect URL
- `hide_form`: Boolean to hide the form

### header_data (Required)
- `tagline`: Main headline
- `sub_heading`: Subtitle
- `background`: Background color
- `tagline_color`: Text color
- `form_styles`: Form styling object
- `background_image`: Hero background image
- `badge`: Optional badge image
- `image_filter`: CSS filter for background image

### follow_bar (Required)
- `position`: "top", "bottom", or "hidden"
- `content.text`: Desktop text content
- `content.text_mobile`: Mobile text content
- `content.font_size`: Array of font sizes for different devices
- `button.text`: Button text
- `button.path`: Button link
- `phone.text`: Phone label
- `phone.number`: Phone number

### features (Required)
- `bullets`: Array of feature bullet points
- `styles`: Optional CSS styles
- `marginTop`: Optional margin

