## Image Requirements
- All images must use relative paths starting with `/images/` or `../../../static/images/`
- Images support `childImageSharp.gatsbyImageData` for optimization
- Image objects can include `src`, `style`, `shadow`, `link` properties

## Component Positioning
- Components are rendered in order based on `position` field (ascending)
- Lower position numbers appear first on the page
- Position values should be spaced (e.g., 1, 2, 5, 10) to allow for future insertions

## Language-Specific Requirements

- Files must use the language specified by the user (e.g., English for .us.yml, Spanish for .es.yml).
- English files (.us.yml): Use English text and "us" language context.
-  Spanish files (.es.yml): Use Spanish text and "es" language context.
-  Each file must follow the structure defined, with no requirement for dual-language versions unless explicitly requested.


